{"tid":2100984,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"雞排妹赴日發展出道！內褲竟滑落到大腿…淚揭「心酸內情」","createTime":"2020-07-09T12:25:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T04:53:07.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"860f1fb13ea50636a2bcefd0124ca118f0b236db","tid":2100984,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:25:33.000Z","msg":"雞排妹（鄭家純）因擁有火辣身材、天使的臉孔，再加上說話風格犀利、作風大膽，，讓她在網路上有相當高的聲量，過去她透露自己為了學習日文，短暫到日本去遊學念語言學校，並且順利在當地發展演藝事業；近日她接受網紅米鹿deerdeer的訪問，分享當時日本遊學的生活，雞排妹自爆在日本最有印象的是「內褲竟穿到掉下來」，而背後原因曝光後，相當心酸。<br />\n<br />\n雞排妹分享當時第二次到日本遊學，因為跟當地一間媒體合作拍片，一週拍一支生活Vlog放在YouTube頻道上，並且跟對方談好，雞排妹自己找素材拍攝，而他們就是負責剪輯後製，沒想到拍完後，素材檔案太大，雞排妹租屋處的網路傳不過去，她只好利用每天傍晚下課後的時間自己學剪片，一剪就剪到零晨三、四點，雞排妹分享平日就是上課，下課後先準備明天日語考試的內容，再來剪片，假日就是排滿拍片行程，相當忙碌。<br />\n<br />\n而這樣的生活維持一個多月，雞排妹表示當時洗完澡要穿衣服時，內褲竟滑落到地上，她心酸表示因為暴瘦，所以連內褲都包不住她骨瘦如材的身體，雞排妹還透露，某一晚剪片剪到睡著，醒來後發現自己癱坐在塑膠椅上，不過雞排妹也表示，因為歷經過這樣的生活，幾乎每個假日都在跟店家交涉拍片，沒時間休息的她，日語因此快速進步很多。"},{"pid":"d928a55f3ba2fc5316d748c86fd6c6df18324c8f","tid":2100984,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:25:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/07/09/2654202-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F07%2F09%2F2654202-XXL.jpg&h=cbfa4498&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲雞排妹分享當時因為拍片而暴瘦，所以連內褲穿了都會掉下來。（圖／翻攝自YT）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/07/09/2654203-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F07%2F09%2F2654203-XXL.jpg&h=505f08f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c76e33c899f9eb3c5b0c665634e3e7f767d0a46","tid":2100984,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:26:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/07/09/2654204-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F07%2F09%2F2654204-XXL.jpg&h=24c7e178&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲雞排妹提到自己在日本時，利用課餘時間拍片、找素材，相當辛苦。（圖／翻攝自YT）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/07/09/2654205-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F07%2F09%2F2654205-XXL.jpg&h=bf62ad17&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f9d695847c039487e3c3340b0c661df4a87135cb","tid":2100984,"uid":53798,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:36:19.000Z","msg":"真係好慘<br />\n有錢收既慘"},{"pid":"7e917cd862d02f17370b234fb844ae7e92207591","tid":2100984,"uid":146285,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:42:26.000Z","msg":"會唔會係著太耐橡筋鬆咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"724f33c0e309f56c4c64bbf87854ca16a48051ca","tid":2100984,"uid":267035,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:44:42.000Z","msg":"想索佢條底底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一定好香"},{"pid":"e2d142952df073232d9f0f091f29b632cdd1ba04","tid":2100984,"uid":118125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9d695847c039487e3c3340b0c661df4a87135cb","tid":2100984,"uid":53798,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:36:19.000Z","msg":"真係好慘<br />\n有錢收既慘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T13:01:25.000Z","msg":"好慘，要資助津貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XY6d7BEQAnY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXY6d7BEQAnY&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmk9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=de9316b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://yo